CHAT.comment: Chi and Mot sit next to each other at a table. Chi is initially very hesitant about starting and , in the end , does not read. Instead , taking EXP's suggestion , Chi interprets the story through the pictures. At times Chi initiates but , at other times , MOT takes the lead and asks questions of Chi. Mot's questions are often based on the text. (what's he looking for? prompting for food) Overall Chi seems to enjoy the activity and sounds quite delighted by certain pictures.

u.a: phone rings; Mot lets machine answer
